snippet.title: Sniper Elite: Nazi Zombie Army 2 (NZA2) - Official Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
PRE-ORDER for just $11.99 / £7.99 / 8.79 Euro (that's 20% off)!

from Steam: http://goo.gl/CyBVST
from Rebellion: http://goo.gl/mT2e0K

Get a dramatic first look at the waves of living dead thirsty for sniper blood, and catch a glimpse of some of the game's grotesque new enemies!
